. Opting for the radiant over a round here gives you a much larger apparent size while saving a mountain of retail capital.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>2.00ct</strong></td><td>~9.0 × 7.0mm</td><td>~8.1mm</td><td>Clearly larger</td><td><strong>10/10 — Trophy-Class Finger Coverage.</strong> Pushing a massive 9mm length completely transforms the ring's design profile. This configuration delivers an incredibly dramatic, high-end "quiet luxury" look on the hand. The elongated outline maximizes your physical coverage per dollar, ensuring absolute hand presence that commands immediate focus.</td></tr></tbody></table>

